<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Successful</title>
    <style>
        /* Pink theme styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffe6f0;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #ff69b4;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .details {
            background-color: #ffcce0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .details h2 {
            color: #ff69b4;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff69b4;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff4a93;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Registration Successful!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for registering, <%= username  %>!</p>
        <p>Your account has been created successfully.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>